				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This is a follow up to my post above.  I asked the question, and now I will answer it.  Charisma definitely affects this spell.  The lower your charisma, the better (like the post above mine says, it makes sense, low charisma = scary mo-fo).<BR>
<BR>
I know this because I acquired a marauder snout ring that lowers your charisma by 20 pts.  I went from 55 char to 35 char.  The difference was enormous.  Fear hardly ever gets resisted now by mobs that con yellow and even white.  If you wanna use this spell, and you should - its a life saver (plus its fun to use), look into items that lower charisma.  Marauder snout ring is great and not too expensive.  Just take it off before you sell/buy because it will affect the price.
				</font>
			</td>

